Ah, how could I forget? I shall not deprive you of your reward, my friend. Here it is, a magical item from my collection. May it prove useful to you in some way.
Greetings to you, my good <lord/lady>. It is rare we see new faces come to drink with us at the Alliance Inn.
If you haven't heard much of Elaith Craulnober, I'll certainly not be the one to educate you. Let the tongues of others guide you as they will, it matters not to me.

One of the gems is in the possession of Wanev, a local wizard. I suspect the gem is secreted away in his tower, which can be found in the grasslands directly east of Port Llast. The tower gates are magically locked and I do not know how they can be opened.

Another gem is held by a fierce warrior woman named Zamithra who passed through several days ago. According to her, she's been pillaging and plundering all around the road towards Highcliff, which could be a lie. However, she does look the type.

I can offer you a decent amount of gold for each of the gems that you return to me. If you bring all three, I will add an additional amount of gold as well as a magic item that I'm sure you'll find a use for.
I have Setara's gem right here.
I have Zamithra's gem right here.
I have Wanev's gem right here.
What about my reward for recovering all the gems?
